#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:131
msgid "Prerelease bump rules:"
msgstr "预发布提升规则："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:133
msgid "Bumping a stable version to `alpha`, `beta`, or `rc` first increments the patch version, then enters the target channel starting from `.1`."
msgstr "将稳定版本提升到 `alpha`、`beta` 或 `rc` 时，会先递增 patch 版本，再进入目标 通道并从 `.1` 开始。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:135
msgid "`prepatch`, `preminor`, and `premajor` start a fresh prerelease from the next patch, minor, or major version respectively, such as `1.2.3 -> 1.3.0-rc.1` with `preminor` + `rc`."
msgstr "`prepatch`、`preminor` 和 `premajor` 会分别从下一个 patch、minor 或 major 版本开始全新的预发布，例如使用 `preminor` + `rc` 时， `1.2.3 -> 1.3.0-rc.1`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:138
msgid "Bumping within the same channel increments the sequence number, such as `alpha.1 -> alpha.2`."
msgstr "在同一通道内继续提升时，会递增序号，例如 `alpha.1 -> alpha.2`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:140
msgid "`release` removes prerelease and build metadata while keeping the same `major.minor.patch` values, such as `1.2.3-rc.2 -> 1.2.3`."
msgstr "`release` 会移除预发布和 build 元数据，同时保持 `major.minor.patch` 不变， 例如 `1.2.3-rc.2 -> 1.2.3`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/semver.md:142
msgid "Channel promotion is allowed (`alpha -> beta -> rc`), but channel downgrade is not (for example, `rc -> beta` raises an error)."
msgstr "允许通道升级（`alpha -> beta -> rc`），但不允许通道降级 （例如 `rc -> beta` 会抛出错误）。"
